				"speakerSlotDescription": [
					{}
				],
				"synopsis": {
					"type": 23,
					"value": "A weary gravekeeper, absolutely exhausted at having to bury so many bodies in recent days. Would be good to have her have typical gallows humour, but be relatively kindhearted and helpful underneath it (though relatively unimportant) She will exclusively hang around the gravekeeper's house, and likely either be found sat and resting or just idly milling around a small area.\r\n\r\nImportant topics:\r\n- Where you can find a shovel\r\n- Killings in Baldur's Gate (with a branch for if it's solved)\r\n- (When you've encountered them) Kobold Looters\r\n- Something to chastise the player if they've gone around digging up graves themselves, probably a HasMet alt?"
				}
			}
		}
